javax.jdo.metadata
Interface ComponentMetadata

All Superinterfaces:
Metadata
All Known Subinterfaces:
ClassMetadata, InterfaceMetadata
public interface ComponentMetadata
extends Metadata

Represents a class or interface. Extended for the specifics of those cases.

Since:
2.3
